title: Yosuke Hanya
text:
is a <a href="Japanese%20people">Japanese</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Career.
Yosuke Hanya joined <a href="FC%20Tokyo">FC Tokyo</a> in 2016. On July 31, he debuted in <a href="J3%20League">J3 League</a> (v <a href="Gainare%20Tottori">Gainare Tottori</a>).
